# infra/production/env/ai.env — AI sidecar model providers (Milestone 18).
# Copy to `ai.env`, fill in, keep out of git. The service token, API base URL,
# and internal token are injected by the Compose profile from ../.env.

# ---- real model provider (Milestone 15, ADR-0023) -------------------------
# Unset keeps the deterministic offline model. Pilot default: Anthropic Claude
# claude-sonnet-5 (2026-07-07 live eval gates green). A provider OR model swap
# must re-run the eval gates before traffic (SOPS §11.1):
#   python -m evals.live_runner
# SUPPORT_LLM_PROVIDER=anthropic
# SUPPORT_LLM_MODEL=claude-sonnet-5
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# SUPPORT_LLM_TIMEOUT_MS=30000
# SUPPORT_LLM_MAX_RETRIES=2
